Kylie Jenner pregnant: Khloe Kardashian 'baby bump' picture convinces fans 20 year old is pregnant with her first child with boyfriend Travis Scott KYLIE Jenner is reported to be five months pregnant with her first baby, but she has not yet confirmed the news.

Kylie Jenner fans are convinced they saw her baby bump on Snapchat [Kylie Jenner/instagram]

Keeping Up With The Kardashians star Kylie Jenner, 20, and her boyfriend Travis Scott are reportedly pregnant with their first child.

With further reports also suggesting Khloe Kardashian is pregnant with boyfriend Tristan Thompson and Kim Kardashian West confirming she is having another baby with a surrogate, the Kardashian and Jenner family are surrounded by baby reports and news updates.

And now, without any word from Kylie or her family about the pregnancy reports, fans are convinced they've seen Kris Jenner's daughter's baby bump for the first time.

Here's everything you need to know about the 'pregnant' Kylie Jenner reports:

People are convinced Kylie Jenner is pregnant with her first child [Getty]

Kylie Jenner baby bump

Fans first believed they spotted Kylie Jenner's baby bump on Snapchat when she shared a clip of herself cuddling up to her pups.

Kylie Jenner 'pregnant': Keeping Up With The Kardashian star's 'pregnancy' pictures Tuesday, November 07, 2017 1 / 16

/





Play slideshow Kylie Jenner 'pregnant': Keeping Up With The Kardashian star's 'pregnancy' pictures Tuesday, November 07, 2017 1 / 16

/

Play slideshow Kylie Jenner's pictured amid ingoing pregnancy speculation [X17online ]





























Kylie Jenner pregnancy rumours have swept the world with Keeping Up With The Kardashians fans convinced she is pregnant with boyfriend Travis Scott – click here to see Kylie Jenner's 'pregnant' pictures



She kept her stomach hidden in a cosy grey hoodie, completing her dressed-down look with a pair of tracksuit bottoms.

However, fans were convinced they could see the reality star’s body changes.

Kylie Jenner and Khloe Kardashian showed off their figures amid pregnancy rumours [Kylie Jenner/Snapchat]

And Kylie has done it again as she went to the shops with Khloe Kardashian dressed in her baggiest outfit yet.

Reports claim Kylie is five months pregnant

According to TMZ, sources directly closest to Kylie and her beau have claimed she’s "five months along", and expecting yet another girl to join the Kardashian clan.

It’s around the exact time that Kim Kardashian is said to be expecting her third child via surrogate.

Kylie Jenner gave fans a glimpse of her stomach [Kylie Jenner/Instagram]

Is this the moment Travis Scott found out?

Fans are convinced they know when Travis Scott found out the 'happy news' from Kylie, who has a huge net worth.

On June 12, the star cryptically tweeted: "Legit the happiest day of my life."

According to Perez Hilton this would coincide perfectly with the reported due date, and the pair went on to get a matching butterfly tattoo.

Travis Scott tweeted a cryptic message back in June [Twitter]

Due date?

According to the unconfirmed reports, Kylie is thought to be four months pregnant, and People magazine is also reporting that Kylie is due to give birth in February 2018.

A source said: “They started telling friends a few weeks ago. The family has known for quite some time. She is really excited and so is Travis!”

Another insider added: “It is an unexpected but completely amazing turn of events that she could not be more excited or thrilled about.

Fans believe Kylie Jenner may have hinted she was pregnant in August [Kylie Jenner/Instagram]

They added: “Everyone is overjoyed for her. This is the happiest she’s ever been.”

Gender?

Despite not talking about the rumoured pregnancy at all, fans have become convinced the reality millionaire will have a baby boy.

Why? Because Kylie has become unusually obsessed with the colour blue since the reports began.

From a baggy blue shirt to a phone cover with blue lip kits on, fans couldn't help but make the connection.

Clues?

Kylie Jenner posted this picture on her Snapchat amid pregnancy speculation [Kylie Jenner/Snapchat]

Kylie's fans are convinced the Kardashian star has given away a series of clues alluding to her 'pregnancy'.

In a recent Snapchat photo the star wore a baggy T-shirt while posing with friends, causing fans to speculate.

Some also believe in another photo posted to her 97 million Instagram followers, she is subtly pointing to her stomach.

Family ambition

Kylie Jenner has always spoken about her desire to have kids [Kylie Jenner/Instagram]

The E! star has previously spoken about her desire to have children sooner rather than later.

In an on-screen conversation with her dad Caitlyn last year, she said: "I feel like 30 is too late [to start a family]. Every psychic said I'm only gonna have two kids."

Fans react

Despite Kris Jenner's very vague response to the reports, Kylie has remained tight lipped on the rumours and fans are begging for answers.

One wrote on Twitter: "It's been 48 hours since the Kylie Jenner scandal and we still have no word. @KylieJenner are you pregnant YES OR NO."

Kylie Jenner has continued to post on Instagram and Snapchat since the rumours broke [Kylie Jenner/Instagram]

Also impatient, another added: "All I want in life right now is for @KylieJenner to confirm if she is pregnant or not."

OK! Online has contacted the representatives for both Kylie and Travis.

Kylie Jenner to pick a unique baby name?

Despite the 20 year old not confirming or denying her pregnancy, reports have already begun speculating about what Kylie would name her future child.

Kylie Jenner is reportedly trying to think of unique baby names [Kylie Jenner/Instagram]

An alleged insider told Hollywood Life: "She would like to do something both unique and keep the 'K' first name consistent with her sisters and mum."

Fans thought she may have gone with the name Butterfly given she and Travis both have matching small butterfly tattoos on their ankles.

Kylie to QUIT social media?

In December 2015 Kylie Jenner told Elle UK she would delete her account as soon as she has a child.

"Once I have a kid I’m not going to be on Instagram," Kylie told the magazine. “You know, I’ll probably delete my Instagram and just… I don’t know, live life.”

Kylie Jenner has left fans convinced she's pregnant with a baby boy [Kylie Jenner / Instagram]

Kylie demands more privacy

According to People magazine, the reason Kylie is being so shy about the reports is because she wants more privacy.

A source told them: "Kylie prefers to stay home. She feels good, but her body is changing. She doesn’t want to be photographed.

"At the moment, she wants more privacy. She has family and friends come to her house instead so she has company."
title: Kylie Jenner fans fully convinced of 'pregnancy' after baby bump spotting
